        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>A spray of rainbow light beams cascades from your open hand. Each creature in the area must roll 1d8 on the table below to see which beam affects it, then attempt a saving throw of the indicated type. The table notes any additional traits that apply to each type of ray. If a creature is struck by multiple beams, it uses the same d20 result for all its saving throws. For all rays, a successful saving throw negates the effect for that creature.</p>\n<h3><strong>Prismatic Spray</strong></h3>\n<table class=\"pf2-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>1d8</th>\n<th>Color</th>\n<th>Save</th>\n<th>Effects (Traits)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>Red</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n<td>50 fire damage (fire)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>Orange</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n<td>60 acid damage (acid)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>Yellow</td>\n<td>Reflex</td>\n<td>70 electricity damage (electricity)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Fortitude</td>\n<td>30 poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 minute (poison)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>Blue</td>\n<td>Fortitude</td>\n<td>Affected as if by @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Flesh to Stone]{Flesh to Stone}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>Indigo</td>\n<td>Will</td>\n<td>Confused, as the @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Warp Mind]{Warp Mind} spell (mental)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>Violet</td>\n<td>Will</td>\n<td>Slowed for 1 minute; if a critical failure, sent to another plane, as @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Plane Shift]{Plane Shift}<em> </em>(teleportation)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>Potent beam</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>Affected by two beams - roll twice, rerolling any duplicates or results of 8</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
